title: Public meeting on toll hikes set despite stay-home order
description: TRENTON, N.J. (AP) — The New Jersey agency that operates the Atlantic City Expressway has scheduled a public meeting for Wednesday to consider toll increase despite the governor's order for residents to stay home during the COVID-19 outbreak.
